  salary and allowances is extended for three months. (ECB Conditions
  of Employment, page 19) - Return to country of origin (resettlement
  benefits):   - Entitlement to termination-of-service benefits
  applies if you resettle more than 50 km from the ECB. (ECB Staff
  Rules, page 72)   - If resettling outside the EU, reimbursement of
  travel and removal expenses is limited to the cost to the capital of
  the EU Member State furthest from the ECB, or the actual costs,
  whichever is lower. (ECB Staff Rules, page 72)   - If the place of
  recruitment was outside the EU, relocation to the place of
